It was located not too long from the zone entrance/exit, by the river. <br>
It was a little little bit slower than a SoW from a 60 shaman, impossible to outrun so much you could snare it without self being in snarerange and getting hit. <br>
I had 3 more snared, decided i didnt feel like risking snaring self so close to evac spot so I ran right into the wood, when i was a bit away from entrance i hit exodus. <br>
<br>
Anyone else experienced SoW speed stuff in PoN, or was this a one time thing?<br>
just hope its not yet another stealthnerf.<br>
